'''''man''''' is a [[Quenya]] word meaning "who".<ref>{{RGEO|Namarie}}, p. 59</ref>

==Examples==
*''[[Namárië|Sí '''man''' i yulma nin enquantuva?]]'' = "'''Who''' now shall refill the cup for me?"
*''[[Markirya|'''man''' cenuva lumbor ahosta?]]'' = "'''Who''' shall see the clouds gather?"

